    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.36.37-38_0001a" />
                
               <opener>
                <dateline>
                Skyrim, Route 7, <lb/>
                Colubmia, Mo.<lb/>
                
                6-20-62
                </dateline>
                
                <salute>Dear Russell Moran:</salute>
               </opener>
                <p>I think I'm as happy about the whole thing as you and Mrs. Weaver are! It's all perfectly bully!</p>
                
                <p>The photo and the note for the dictionary are on the way to you. Checkmarks indicate where you and Mrs. Weaver are to sign the document!</p> 
                
                <p>I'm indeed glad
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.36.37-38_0001b"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw><fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                    
                    to know about your new position and Mrs. W's too.</p>
                
                <p>Next year I'll be giving my <hi rend="underline">Epic America</hi> course in two sections by <hi rend="caps">TV.</hi>. The classes have been rather too large and we want to take more students with smaller classes.</p>
                
                <p>Here are my kindest thoughts and best wishes for Mrs.
                    
                    <fw type="curatorial">37</fw>
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.36.37-38_0002"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-3-</fw>
                    
                    Weaver and yourself.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Your friend,</salute>
                
                <signed>John Neihardt</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript><p>Thanks for the check &#8212; but you could just as well <add>have</add> kept it. And many thanks for the photo of Slade and me.</p>
                
                <closer><signed>J. N.</signed></closer></postscript>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
